  {
    "hotel_id": "10535495",
    "hotel_url": "https://www.agoda.com/icon-saigon-luxury-design-hotel/hotel/ho-chi-minh-city-vn.html",
    "name": "Icon Saigon - LifeStyle Design Hotel",
    "detail": "Icon is a small boutique hotel with luxurious features in a very convenient, central location of District 1 in Ho Chi Minh City, close to tourist attractions and restaurants. Despite its size, it is jam-packed with goodies like a nice rooftop with a swimming pool and a bar. The breakfast was also high quality. Only thing to keep in mind is that some of the rooms do not have windows facing outside. In these rooms, the windows open up to the vents with open roof. But even these rooms has positive features like completely shutting off the hustle and bustle of busy HCMC traffic noise and city lights, which allows for good night's rest. I happened to actually enjoy the dark and quiet features of the room, especially since I was travelling with a jet lag. ",
